Interface VorbisLibrary

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.sun.jna.Library, XiphLibrary

    public interface VorbisLibrary
extends XiphLibrary
    JNA wrapper for libvorbis. Includes codec.h, vorbisenc.h, vorbisfile.h
